🔁 End-to-End Flow
Code pushed to GitHub
GitHub Actions triggers pipeline
Run tests + security scans (SAST, dependencies)
Build Docker image
Scan container image
Push to registry
Deploy to Kubernetes / cloud
Run DAST (runtime testing)

🔐 Security Integrated at Every Stage

1. SAST (Static Code Analysis)
          Tool: CodeQL

👉 Finds vulnerabilities in source code before build

2. Dependency Scanning
          Tools:  Dependabot, Snyk

👉 Detects vulnerable libraries (CVEs)

3. Secrets Management
          Use GitHub Secrets
👉 Prevents hardcoding credentials 

4. Container Security
          Tool: Trivy

👉 Scans Docker images before deployment

5. DAST (Runtime Security)
          Tool: OWASP ZAP

👉 Tests running app for real-time vulnerabilities
